headline: Newsweek Names The Campbell’s Company One of America’s Greatest Workplaces
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., June 04, 2025--The Campbell's Company (NASDAQ:CPB ) today announced that Newsweek has named the company one of America’s Greatest Workplaces 2025.

headline: Tariff uncertainty is hammering one of America's favorite food escapes — snacks
summary: The snacking industry has been under pressure as consumers pull back on impulse purchases amid rising prices and economic uncertainty.
